To be fair, we've only tried the pizza. It was fine, as pizza goes. But as far as New haven pizza goes? Not even in the top 3. They have lots of trendy, cute 'artisinal" toppings but that's not what makes a great apizza. It's the crust, pure and simple, and they fall short of Modern or Pepe's, perhaps rivalling only the other top place in town, Sally's
